{
  "texts": [
    "They demonstrate the diverse ways AI is advancing olfactory research.",
    "AI techniques, especially deep learning, allow for more accurate modeling of odor perception and the prediction of odorant interactions.",
    "This enhances applications like flavor profiling and environmental sensing.",
    "AI-driven wearable systems are also highlighted.",
    "These systems have the potential to revolutionize personalized sensory experiences."
  ]
